               <head xml:lang="en">Create a corpus of useful resources for the dictionary.</head>
               <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">These resrouces can be corpora as well as other
                  dictionaries, used as references or direct sources to build the dictionary.
                  Depending on the cases, this step may require digitizing printed text (see the
                  related scenario on <ref type="link"
                     target="http://ssk.huma-num.fr/#/scenarios/SSK_sc_digitization"
                     >digitization</ref>), and/or build a normalized and lemmatized corpus (see <ref
                     type="link"
                     target="http://ssk.huma-num.fr/#/scenarios/SSK_sc_corpusModellingInTEI/8"
                     >here</ref> the related scenario).</desc>
